        </p>

        <h3>🔐 Example Request</h3>
        <pre><code class="http">
         POST /api/ShareApi/GetShareData?ApiKey={your-api-key}
         Authorization: Bearer {your-token}
         Content-Type: application/json

         {
           "pageSize": 10,
           "pageIndex": 1,
           "orderBy": "",
           "ascending":true
         }
         </code></pre>
